    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Mehs grabbſtam pehz\ntahs Seenas/ ka tee Aklee/ un\nitt ka tee/ kam Azzu newaid/ ta\ngrabbſtain mehs/ mehs peedan-\nsamees Deenas. Widdû itt ka\nKrehſlibâ/ mehs eſtam pohſtas\nWeetâs ka tee Nomirruschee."
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Mehs tubzam wiſſi ka nibu ka\nPahtſchi/ mehs watdam waide-\ndami itt ka Balloſchi/ mehs gat-\ndam us Teefu/ bet newaid/ ue\nPestischanu/ bet ta irr no mums\ntahfu."
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo muhſas Pahrkahp-\nchanas irr leelas preeſch tewim/\nun muhſu Grehki dohd prett\nmums Leezibu. Jo muhſu Pahr-\nkahpſchanas irr pee mums/ un\nmehs paſihſtam muhſu Noſee-\ngimus."
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ar Pahrkahpschann un\nMelleem prett to KUNGU/ ar\nAtpakkat-Greetchanu no muhſu\nDeewa/ ar Kunnaſchann no\nApbehdiſchanas/ un Atkahp-\nchanas/ ar Eeenmschann/\nun Iſdohmaſchanu nepateefu\nWahrdü no Sirdeſdibbina."
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta Teefa irr arridſan at-\npakkat greeuſees/ nn ta Taifni-\nba stahw no tahſenes/ jo ta Pa-\nteeſiba ſtraipale us Gelu/ un tas\nTeefa irr/ tas ne warr ee-eet."
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Teefcham/ ta Patceſiba KUNGU:"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "irr nohſt/ un kas no Launa at-\nkahpj/ tas darrahs pats par Lan-\npijumu. To reds tas KUNGS/\nun tas winnam ne patihſ/ ka\nTeefa ne irratd."
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch reds/ ka ne-\nweens klaht irr/ tapehz wiꞥſch\nbrihntjahs/ ka Aisſahwetaja ne-\nwaid. Tapehz patihdsahs wiꞥſch\npats ar fawu Elkonn/ un winna\nTaifniba ueſurr winnu."
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo wiꞥſch apweik Taif-\nnibu ka Kruhſchu Bruunas/\nun to Bruunu Zeppuri tahs\nPestischanas ( leeſ wiꞥſch ) us\nfawn Galwu/ un tahs Atreep-\nchanas Drebbes ueweik wiꞥſch\npar Apgehrbu/ un apmett to\nkarſtu Duſmoschann ka weenu\nMehteli."
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Itt ka tee Nopelmi biju-\nſchi/ tapatt wiꞥſch atmakkahs/\nBahrfibu ſaweem Prettinee-\nkeem/ Atmakkaſchanu ſaweem\nEenaideekeem/ tahm Sallahm\natmakkahs wiꞥſch pehz Nopel-\nneem."
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad tee bihſees ta KUNG-\nGA Wahrdü no Wakkara Puſ-\nſes/ un no Saules Uslehſcha-\nnas winna Gohdibu/ tad tas\nErnaidneeks nahks ka Uppe/ tad\niszels ta KUNGU Gars to Kar-\nrogu prett winnu."
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un weens Peſtitajs nahks\nuhs Zianu/ un teein/ kas atgree-\nschahs no tahs Pahrkahpſchanas\neekſch Jehkaba/ fatta tas\nKUNGU:"
    }
  ],
